The paper discusses differentially private algorithms for machine learning classification, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also discusses privacy concerns and the use of private data, which could fall under "Cryptography and Security" (cs.CR). The paper also discusses feature selection and ROC curve construction, which could fall under "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS), "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), and "Databases" (cs.DB).
